/span>\r\n                                                            <dl>\r\n                                                                <dt><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/history\" target=\"_self\">历史</a></dt>\r\n                                                                <dd>\r\n                                                                    <ul>\r\n                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/history/sc-history\" target=\"_self\">追溯住友的历史</a></li>\r\n                                                                    </ul>\r\n                                                                </dd>\r\n                                                            </dl>\r\n                                                        </li>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/network\" target=\"_self\">全球网络</a></li>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/governance\" target=\"_self\">治理</a></li>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/talent\" target=\"_self\">人力资本</a></li>\r\n                                        </ul>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <span>\r\n                            主营业务\r\n                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"u-pc-none\"></button>\r\n                        </span>\r\n                        <div class=\"l-mnavi\">\r\n                            <div class=\"c-inr\">\r\n                                <p class=\"l-mnavi__ttl u-sp-none\">主营业务</p>\r\n                                    <div class=\"l-mnavi__menu\">\r\n                                        <ul>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/business/division-summary\" target=\"_self\">事业领域</a></li>\r\n                                        </ul>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <ul class=\"l-gnavi__lang u-sp\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"/ja/global/about/message\">日本語</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/global/about/message\">英語</a></li>\n<li class=\"is-current\"><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/message\">中文（简体字）</a></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n<div class=\"l-header__search u-sp-none\">\r\n    <button type=\"button\"></button>\r\n    <div class=\"l-header__search__form c-wrap\">\r\n        <div class=\"c-inr\">\r\n            <form name=\"SS_searchForm\" id=\"ss-form1\" action=\"/zhcn/global/search\" method=\"get\">\n    <button class=\"siteSearch-button\" type=\"submit\"></button>\n    <input class=\"siteSearch-input\" id=\"ss-query1\" type=\"text\" name=\"query\" placeholder=\"请输入关键词\" />\n</form>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <main class=\"l-main theme-single theme-second theme-GHQ\">\r\n    <article class=\"l-article\">\r\n        \r\n    <div class=\"fxb-section\">\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-container-fruid\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"mainVisual mainVisual-basic\">\r\n                        <div class=\"_cover\">\r\n                            <div class=\"_trim\"><img src=\"/global/-/media/Images/global/VisualCarousel/mv_item02_pc.jpg?h=550&amp;iar=0&amp;w=1400\" class=\"fit-image\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"550\" /></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"_content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"_catch\">\r\n                                <h1 class=\"_largeTitle\"><span class=\"visible-mobile\">社长兼CEO 的致辞</span></h1>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"fxb-section bg-blueLighter border-top-grayLight\" id=\"breadcrumb\">\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-container\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"breadcrumbs\">\r\n                        <ol>\r\n\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                    <a itemprop=\"item\" href=\"/zhcn/global/\">\r\n                                            <span itemprop=\"name\">主页</span>\r\n                                    </a>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"1\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                        <span itemprop=\"name\">关于我们</span>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"2\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                        <span itemprop=\"name\">社长兼CEO 的致辞</span>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"3\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-section  bg-md-transparent \" id=\"\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-container-fluid\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n<section class=\"layer-title visible-desktop\">\n  <h2 class=\"_largeTitle\">社长兼CEO 的致辞</h2>\n</section>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-section  \" id=\"\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-container\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\" >\r\n                        <p class=\"mt-larger-contain\">受地缘政治风险加剧、供应链格局调整以及人工智能快速发展等因素影响，我们所处的环境正以前所未有的速度持续演变，不确定性进一步攀升。</p>\n\n<p>住友商事集团为应对这一变化，充分活用在各地区及多元业务领域所积累的经验和专业知识、商业网络及构想创新能力，在继续强化优势业务的同时，致力于提升自身应对环境变化的能力及灵活性。</p>\n<p>2025财年，本公司实现当期纯利润6,003亿日元，创下历史新高。这既是在《中期经营计划2026》框架下稳步推进各项举措所结出的硕果，更离不开股东、投资者、合作伙伴、所在社会地域以及员工等利益相关方的信任与支持。</p>\n<p><a class=\"link-angle-arrow-right\" href=\"/zhcn/global/about/principles/mid-term\">中期经营计划2026（英语）</a>已进入收官之年。本经营计划的核心目标是强化自身的竞争优势、通过解决社会课题实现成长，以此打造 &ldquo;No.1业务集群&rdquo;。为此，我们将在继续巩固竞争优势的同时，稳步推进资产优化和业务升级，不断提升事业组合的整体质量。</p>\n<p>此外，我们认为数字化和人工智能的进步将带来重大的成长机遇，因此本集团制定了DAIS（Digital & AI Strategy：数字化与人工智能战略），全面推进整个集团的业务变革。我们依托各业务一线沉淀的经验知识和数字化解决方案的深度融合，以灵活的创新思维和高效的执行能力，推动社会与产业的变革。</p>\n<p>住友商事集团以住友的事业精神及集团经营理念为基础，践行 <a class=\"link-angle-arrow-right\" href=\"/zhcn/global/about/corporate-message\" style=\"padding-left: 15px;\">&ldquo;Enriching lives and the world&rdquo;</a>&nbsp;这一企业宣言。在进一步深化与利益相关方的信任关系的同时，我们将通过健全的业务活动为解决社会课题作出贡献，并实现集团的可持续发展。</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-medium-contain\">今后也恳请各位继续给予住友商事集团一如既往的理解与支持。</p>\n\n<div class=\"signatureArea\">\n  <p class=\"text-weight-bold\">代表取缔役 社长执行董事CEO<br>\n    上野 真吾</p>\n</div>\r\n                        \r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"l-lnavi c-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-inr\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"l-lnavi__ttl u-f--dmst\">关于我们</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"l-lnavi__menu\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n        <li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/corporate-mess